# im5

Explain a concept in simpler terms. Reduce jargon. A person new to the discipline should be able to understand what you're saying.

## Usage

```
/im5                    # Explain the most recent response
/im5 <description>      # Explain what the user describes
```

## What You Must Do When Invoked

1. Establish a brief baseline understanding of the situation
2. Then build off the baseline explaining in plain terms
3. If a visual would help, create an html file for the user that clearly explains the concept (only do this when necessary and use an Opus subagent)

